Executive Profile
Dominic James Addesso CPAChief Executive Officer, President and Non-Independent Director, Everest Re Group, Ltd.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 6 different industries.See Board Relationships63$8,827,677As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Dominic James Addesso, also known as Dom, CPA serves as the President of Everest Reinsurance Company. Mr. Addesso has been the Chief Executive Officer of Everest Re Group Ltd. since January 1, 2014 and as its President since June 16, 2011. He serves as the Chief Executive Officer of Everest National Insurance Company. Mr. Addesso served as the Chief Financial Officer of Everest Re Group Ltd. since May 8, 2009. He serves as the Chairman, Chief Executive Officer and ... President of Everest Reinsurance Holdings Inc. He is the Director and Treasurer at Everest Insurance Company of Canada. Mr. Addesso served as an Executive Vice President at Everest Re Group Ltd. and Everest Reinsurance Holdings Inc. from May 8, 2009 to June 16, 2011. He served as Chief Financial Officer of Everest Reinsurance Holdings Inc. Since joining American Re in 1997, he has held various positions and served as its Senior Vice President, responsible for regional markets in American Re''s direct U.S. insurance company operations and as Senior Vice President in American Re Financial Products, overseeing all financial reinsurance business and certain capital market activities. He provides, directly to U.S. insurance companies, traditional and finite risk reinsurance products and services on a treaty basis. Mr. Addesso served as the President of American Re Direct Treaty at Munich Reinsurance America Inc. since March 26, 2002. Prior to joining Munich Reinsurance America, Inc. in 1997, he served as the Chief Financial Officer of Selective Insurance Group. He has more than 30 years insurance industry experience with broad knowledge across the financial and operating disciplines of a company. Mr. Addesso has been a Director of Everest Re Group Ltd. since September 19, 2012. Mr. Addesso is a Certified Public Accountant and a member of the New Jersey Society of CPAs and the American Institute of CPAs. Mr. Addesso is a graduate from the University of Notre Dame.Read Full Background




