Dominic James Addesso, CPA

Age : 63Public asset : 20,674,999 USDLinked companies :  Everest Re Group Ltd 





Summary 



Mr. Dominic J. Addesso, CPA, is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Everest Global Services, Inc., Chairman at Everest Re Advisors Ltd., Chairman & President at Mt. Whitney Securities, Inc., President & Chief Executive Officer at Everest National Insurance Co., Chairman at Everest International Reinsurance Ltd., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Everest Reinsurance Holdings, Inc., Chairman at Everest Reinsurance (Bermuda) Ltd., a Member at New Jersey Society of Certified Public Accountants and a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants.He is on the Board of Directors at Everest Advisors (UK) Ltd., Everest Indemnity Insurance Co., Everest Security Insurance Co., Mt. McKinley Insurance Co., Everest Re Group Ltd. and Everest Reinsurance Co. Mr. Addesso was previously employed as Treasurer & Director by Everest Insurance Co. of Canada, President-Regional Clients by Munich Reinsurance America, Inc., and Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Selective Insurance Group, Inc.He also served on the board at Everest Reinsurance Co. (Ireland) Ltd. and Everest Underwriting Group (Ireland) Ltd.He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Notre Dame.



